
DO SPRING CHANGES:
1. get most recent phpBB
	wget https://www.phpbb.com/files/release/phpBB-3.0.12.tar.bz2
	tar xifz phpBB-3.0.12.tar.bz2
2. apply SPRING.patch to it and hope it works:
	cd phpBB3
	patch -p1 < phpbb/SPRING.patch)
3. update SPRING.patch:
	cd ..
	diff -ruN -x  "mobiquo" -x "cache" -x "files" -x "images" -x "styles" -x "docs" -x "install" -x ".install" -x "SPRING.patch" phpBB3/ phpbb/
4. copy data files to new phpbb:
	cp -rv phpbb/mobiqo/ phpBB3/
	cp -rv phpbb/styles/spring/ phpBB3/styles/spring/
	cp -rv phpbb/images/smilies/ phpBB3/images/smilies/
5. use new phpbb:
	rm -rf phpbb
	mv phpBB3 phpbb

UPDATE PHP MYSQL DB:
7. you should have a install folder in your new phpBB install,
   open it from a browser (http://myspringrts.com/phpbb/install/database_update.php)
8. mv install .install (or just remove it)

DONE
9. delete old phpBB install if wanted
10. finished
